text: Chilca may refer to: ==Places in Peru== * Chilca District, Huancayo, Peru, a district in the province of Huancayo. * Chilca, Huancayo, Peru, a city in the province of Huancayo. * Chilca District, Cañete, Peru, a district in the province of Cañete. * Chilca, Cañete, Peru, a city in the province of Cañete. ==Science and Technology== * Chilca Launch Range, a rocket launch test site in the Peruvian province of Cañete.
